{"tid":1449250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:57:41.000Z","uid":204919,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de25700a8e969269169acac64dfebd1f7030d9ef","tid":1449250,"uid":204919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpoHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=6d29492d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpoHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=b612a460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"b7ccd8eb2e2529b5574eabda4e66c2dbfc2ef9ae","tid":1449250,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:51:13.000Z","msg":"721 811 解散警隊"},{"pid":"ffa36e9d32910ba34ade553e885a03af0b813134","tid":1449250,"uid":268498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:52:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"43cd2a343cfe0b3e54f474cfb7728de3f3bc27b0","tid":1449250,"uid":12020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:55:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd77a325541c088a53a7ee664e30e4e3e89eedc6","tid":1449250,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:57:41.000Z","msg":